      <para id="id1164090248155">Specifications</para>
      <list id="id1164089113617" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>The specifications that follow below will be relevant to your design: You could add your own specifications – perhaps with some help from your educator!</item>
      </list>
      <list id="id1164088813469" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Climbing frames must be functional</item>
        <item>They must be safe</item>
        <item>Wood or drinking straws can be used to construct the model (ice-cream sticks can be used effectively)</item>
        <item>The model must not be larger than A4-size paper (length, height and width designed to scale)</item>
        <item>It must be affordable (do not plan to use an unnecessarily large quantity of materials)</item>
      </list>
