      <para id="id1164090204179">Research</para>
      <list id="id1164092245709" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>You have to obtain information regarding the following:</item>
      </list>
      <list id="id1164090447568" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Various designs for climbing frames;</item>
        <item>Various methods of construction using sticks made from wood;</item>
        <item>The types of glue to use for wood and for drinking straws;</item>
        <item>What you could use to make a swing;</item>
        <item>The tools that you will need, and the purpose of each tool.</item>
      </list>
